intent_template: Can you add {description} to my cart?
intent: Can you add enough of this item to come out to more than the first item added in the video to my cart?
intermediate_intent: How much did the first item added to cart in the video cost in dollars?

instantiation_dict.description: enough of this item to come out to more than the first item added in the video

must_include: Sunset Jade Plant - Crassula - Easy to Grow House Plant - 4" Pot

program_html.locator: lambda:(() => {try {return Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('.item-info')).find(el => el.textContent.includes('Sunset Jade Plant - Crassula - Easy to Grow House Plant - 4" Pot')).querySelector('input').getAttribute('data-item-qty')} catch (e) {return ' '}})()
